<h4><a href="https://www.theverge.com/2020/8/27/21402493/amazon-halo-band-health-fitness-body-scan-tone-emotion-activity-sleep">亚马逊推出健康手环 Halo，不带屏幕</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1361502" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Halo_App_and_Halo_Band.0.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Halo_App_and_Halo_Band.0.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Halo_App_and_Halo_Band.0-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Halo_App_and_Halo_Band.0-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Halo_App_and_Halo_Band.0-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>The Verge 消息，亚马逊推出健康手环 Halo，定价 99.99 美元，独立配套订阅服务为 3.99 美元/月。和其它健康手环/智能手表不同的是，Halo 并不搭载屏幕，需结合手机应用使用。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1361503" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Halo_App_Body_Feature.jpg" alt="" width="1120" height="746" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Halo_App_Body_Feature.jpg 1120w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Halo_App_Body_Feature-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Halo_App_Body_Feature-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Halo_App_Body_Feature-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1120px) 100vw, 1120px" /></p>
<p>除了追踪常规的心率、睡眠等数据外，Halo 最大特点在于可结合手机应用，利用手机摄像头扫描用户身体，并以此计算体脂率；此外，通过手环上的麦克风，Halo 也能判断用户一天里的情绪变化。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.theverge.com/2020/8/27/21403762/lg-puricare-wearable-air-purifier-mask-coronavirus-filter">LG 发布穿戴式空气净化器，长得就像口罩一样</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1361504" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/LG-PuriCare-Wearable-Air-Purifier-LIFESTYLE.jpg" alt="" width="1417" height="809" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/LG-PuriCare-Wearable-Air-Purifier-LIFESTYLE.jpg 1417w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/LG-PuriCare-Wearable-Air-Purifier-LIFESTYLE-360x206.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/LG-PuriCare-Wearable-Air-Purifier-LIFESTYLE-768x438.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/LG-PuriCare-Wearable-Air-Purifier-LIFESTYLE-1024x585.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1417px) 100vw, 1417px" /></p>
<p>The Verge 消息，LG 正式发布可穿戴式空气净化器 PURICARE。它采用了和 LG 家用空气净化器一样的滤芯，搭载的电扇将根据佩戴者「呼」和「吸」的动作来调整风率，保持舒适度。</p>
<p>值得指出的是，当被问及净化器对抗新冠病毒的能力，官方拒绝正式回应，表示他们正在等待相关测试和认证结果。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293889" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1021277.htm">AirPods 的市场份额正在被蚕食</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1361505" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/5db8ac8cdee0196e683af782.jpeg" alt="" width="1100" height="733" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/5db8ac8cdee0196e683af782.jpeg 1100w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/5db8ac8cdee0196e683af782-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/5db8ac8cdee0196e683af782-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/5db8ac8cdee0196e683af782-1024x682.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1100px) 100vw, 1100px" /></p>
<p>cnBeta 援引市场研究机构 Counterpoint Research 数据指出，苹果的 AirPods 在无线蓝牙耳机市场份额在被其它品牌蚕食。在 2020 年第二季度，AirPods 占市场 35%，低于 2019 年将近 50% 份额。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1361506" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/0bd3d956aee8bb0.png" alt="" width="538" height="280" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/0bd3d956aee8bb0.png 538w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/0bd3d956aee8bb0-360x187.png 360w" sizes="(max-width: 538px) 100vw, 538px" /></p>
<p>Counterpoint Research 表示，越来越多品牌进入该品类，很多都宣称能提供更低价格、更好体验和更好音质，「更别提三星也为新发布的 Galaxy Buds Live 引入了漂亮的豆形设计和优秀的降噪功能，且售价仅为 170 美元。」</p>
<p>此外，森海塞尔、拜亚动力、铁三角等传统高端音频大厂未能及时把握住这一潮流，Counterpoint 研究人员预计它们的份额低于 0.3% 。</p>
<h4>小鹏汽车在纽交所上市，开盘涨 56%</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1361507" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2020_0827_1b5de331j00qfq9ln00d7c001t400u0c.jpg" alt="" width="2344" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2020_0827_1b5de331j00qfq9ln00d7c001t400u0c.jpg 2344w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2020_0827_1b5de331j00qfq9ln00d7c001t400u0c-360x166.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2020_0827_1b5de331j00qfq9ln00d7c001t400u0c-768x354.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/2020_0827_1b5de331j00qfq9ln00d7c001t400u0c-1024x472.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2344px) 100vw, 2344px" /></p>
<p>36kr 消息，昨晚，小鹏汽车正式登陆纽交所，股票代码「XPEV」，开盘报 23 美元，涨 56%，市值现超 175 亿美元。</p>
<p>小鹏汽车登陆纽交所，意味着中国造车新势力三强齐聚美股市场。</p>
<h4>OPPO 与美洲电信达成战略合作</h4>
<p>OPPO 与拉丁美洲最大电信运营商美洲电信（América Móvil）近日共同宣布，双方已签订战略合作协议，正式建立合作伙伴关系。</p>
<p>OPPO 手机将通过美洲电信旗下运营商进入墨西哥和其他拉美市场，进一步开拓拉美市场潜力。</p>
